<section class="home">
  <h2>Hello</h2>
  <p>I'm a software engineer living in San Francisco. I work as a freelancer. You can <a href="http://hire.soff.es" rel="external nofollow">hire me</a>. Most of my days are spent writing Objective-C and Ruby. In my free time, I make this app called <a href="https://roon.io" rel="external nofollow">Roon</a>&mdash;it's the easiest way to blog. <a href="https://twitter.com/soffes" rel="external nofollow">Say hi.</a></p>

  <% if @post && @post.length > 0 %>
  <h2>Latest Writing</h2>
  <article>
    <h3><a href="<%= @post['url'] %>"><%= @post['title'] %></a></h3>
    <%= @post['excerpt_html'] %>
    <p><a href="<%= @post['url'] %>">Continue Reading &rarr;</a></p>
  </article>
  <% end %>

